&C---------------------======{&WCrimson II NEWS&C}======---------------------&n
This is in summary form. Te see the latest changes check out 'help changelog'

 &W Q2 2024 -
   &w*&n Zone Update:
     - Draconia updated to prevent mobs from wandering to other zones.
     - Nedragaard Keep updated to prevent mobs from wandering to other zones.
   &w*&n Code Update:
     - Paladin: Removed good align requirement. Must maintain strong good or
       evil align or suffer. Gave Energy Drain and Holy Healing at level 4
       to assist with maintaining alignment
     - Druid: Thornwrack modified to be a backstab like effect may need to
       be balanced further. Wrath of Nature changed to always area effect.
     - Race restrictions preventing Demon, Ravshi and Darkling from being
       Paladin removed
     - NOADVANCE flag - locks a character to their current level.
	 - Stave and Wand code fix.
	 - Crash bug fix related to 'get all.coins' when at max gold.

 &W 2021 - 2023 Summary -
   &w*&n Code Update: 
     - Fixed Dancing sword to only transform weapons
     - Fix ability to load bows/crossbows. Updated helpfile with new command
     - Class HP, Mana, Move gain on level works now
     - QOL Changes (Mortal Regen Rate, Rush Hour Frequency, Class Criticals)
	 - Bug Fixes
     - Spell Identify and Auction ID now show average damage on weapons
     - Consider command updated to be more accurate and have better messages
	 - Questmaster will no longer assign quests to mobs in NO_DONATE rooms
     - Added Code to try to resolve zone reboot crashing
     - Changed Quest Items able to be bought from Questmaster
     - Changed Quest Items that can be rewarded from Questmaster
     - Typo Fixes
     - Removed most race/class restrictions(evil races can't be paladin)
     - Adjusted XP rewards from Questmaster
     - Added new Tailed Race "Saurian" See help race 31 for info.
   &w*&n Zone Update:
     - Fixed path to Glass Cathedral to match the Zone description
	&w*&n Server Update:
     - Moved to new Virtual Private Server IP 135.148.148.72
     - New Character Creation closed on old server as of Dec.1 2021
     - Soft Player Wipe with the server move. (We will reimburse one char/kit) 

 &W 2007 - 2020 Summary -
   &w*&n Code Update: 
     - Added and balanced Druid, Monk and Eldritch Knight classes
     - Updated and added helpfiles
     - New Spells and Skills
     - Fixed elemental bits on dual wield weapons
     - Avatar foreign spell limit increased to 55
     - Fixed various bugs
     - Added Vex to BLESS command for evil players
     - Made Pets and Summons act like Gate mobs when leader is gone
     - Changed naming for Immortal channels and mudmail groups
   &w*&n Zone Update:
     - QuelSithElves updated with new quest
     - Tuscany2 new item added.
     - Narsil Sword Quest added to Halfling. Talk to local gossips in Zone
     - Four Horseman of the Apocalypse are roaming the MUD
     - NewbieVillage, GnomeVillage, GerinsTower, RealmOfKhorne, DragonRealm3,
       HadesCastle and DarkCastle have had EQ, Rooms and Mobs updated
   &w*&n Questmaster Update:
     - Items changed, Bow/Crossbow(s) have been improved for hold slot
